So a quick recap on mediation.

00:01:17.370 --> 00:01:19.620
Mediation allows you
to maximize revenue

00:01:19.620 --> 00:01:22.990
by calling multiple ad networks
from a single platform.

00:01:22.990 --> 00:01:24.830
This helps ensure
there is always

00:01:24.830 --> 00:01:27.280
an ad to show in
your application

00:01:27.280 --> 00:01:29.720
