00:01:32.460 --> 00:01:35.280
At AdMob, we want
to build a platform

00:01:35.280 --> 00:01:37.710
to support all your
monetization needs.

00:01:37.710 --> 00:01:40.740
Rewarded has been a
gap, and I'm really

00:01:40.740 --> 00:01:43.760
happy to announce that,
today, we're closing that gap.

00:01:43.760 --> 00:01:45.710
This afternoon,
rewarded mediation

00:01:45.710 --> 00:01:48.520
